Letter Engine

The “Letter to Garcia” idea you’ve used repeatedly can become a reusable mission protocol.

Each Letter contains:

Mission

One concrete objective.

Why

Mission alignment.

Success Criteria

Observable completion.

Dependencies

What must already exist.

Deliverables

What is produced.

Validation

How success is measured.

Spawn Rules

If completed, what new missions become available?

